<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title></title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>按钮（标签button直接用class即可）</h1>
		<button class="btn btn-red">保存</button> 
		<button class="btn btn-red">下一步</button>
		<button class="btn btn-blue">取消</button>
		<button class="btn btn-gray">禁用</button>
		<button class="btn-select">选择图片</button>
		<button class="btn-select-disable">不可操作</button>
		<button class="btn-select btn-select-active">所选操作</button>
		
		<h1>字体颜色（注意样式提示）</h1>
		<h2>搜索和表单部分：</h2>
		<div class="clearfix">
			<dl>
				<dt>dt里的字体颜色：#5e5e5e:</dt>
				<dd>
					<input value="input:{height: 24px; line-height: 24px; color:#7e7e7e; border:1px solid #c7c7c7; padding:0 10px;}宽度不同页面有所区别" type="text"/>
					<p>这里是错误提示p{ line-height: 17px; color: #e06a2f;}</p>
				</dd>
			</dl>
			<dl>
				<dt>dt里的字体颜色：#5e5e5e:</dt>
				<dd>
					<textarea>textarea:{line-height: 24px; color:#7e7e7e; border:1px solid #c7c7c7; padding:5px 10px; resize: none;}宽高不同页面有所区别</textarea>
					<p>这里是错误提示p</p>
				</dd>
			</dl>
		</div>
		<h2>表格部分</h2> 
		<h5>表头统计 <span style=" color: #5e5e5e;">累计交易金额span{color:#5e5e5e}：&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="color: #2fadbc;">￥128.26 strong{color:#2fadbc;}</strong></span></h5>
		<table>
			<tr style="background: #e8eff0; border-bottom: 1px solid #c8d2d4; border-top: 1px solid #c8d2d4;">
				<th style="height: 40px; line-height: 40px; color: #5f6a6c; text-align: left;">表头{height: 40px; line-height: 40px; color: #5f6a6c; text-align: left; background: #e8eff0; border-bottom: 1px solid #c8d2d4; border-top: 1px solid #c8d2d4}</th>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="color: #6b6a6a; border-bottom: 1px solid #d0d0d0; padding: 6px 20px 6px 0; word-wrap: break-word;
    word-break: break-all;">
					表格默认文字颜色：#6b6a6a;border-bottom: 1px solid #d0d0d0; padding: 6px 20px 6px 0; word-wrap: break-word;
    word-break: break-all;<br />
					<span style="color: #888;">浅颜色文字颜色：span{color: #888;}</span><br />
					<strong style="color: #3db9c8; font-weight: normal;">突出文字颜色（蓝色）：strong{color: #3db9c8; font-weight: normal;}</strong>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>  
		<h2>图片列表部分</h2>
		<p class="book">书名&默认文字颜色：{color: #707070;}------>:hover{ color:#2fadbc}</p>
		<p style="color: #5e5e5e;">下载量{color:#5e5e5e; font-size:12px;}：<span style="color: #d9624f;">{color:#d9624f;font-size:12px;}</span></p>

		
		
		
		
	</body>
</html>
